Module fitnessclubgui.fitnessclub
Package fitnessclubgui.fitnessclub

Class Schedule

java.lang.Object
fitnessclubgui.fitnessclub.Schedule
public class Schedule extends Object
Schedule holds an array of fitness classes. Members and their guest can be added and removed from the schedule of individual fitness classes.
